## whether have loan
account= account%>%mutate(have_loan = is.na(account$loan_amount))

#New facet label names for variables
have_cards.labs <-c('have_cards','no_cards')
names(have_cards.labs)<-c('TRUE','FALSE')
have_loan.labs <-c('have_loan','no_loan')
names(have_loan.labs)<-c('TRUE','FALSE')
#create a scatter plot

account %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_point(aes(x=account_id,y=avg_balance,color=have_cards,shape=have_loan))+
  facet_grid(have_loan~have_cards,scales = "free_x",labeller = labeller(have_cards = have_cards.labs, have_loan = have_loan.labs))+
  labs(title = "Scatter Plot of Average Balance of Different Credit Card and Loan Situation") +
  xlab("Account_id") +
  ylab("Average Balance")
